{"id":"4d30bb02-fe9d-4380-8906-37540df1fdec","name":"Sogun | Shit, My Roommate’s My Worst Enemy?!","description":"<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://files.catbox.moe/6ygrmy.png\" alt=\"\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\"> <img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/ce6de49c-6347-4e99-8f00-1d36cba1a735_424ca41e-21d3-4606-8b3c-c95b91154625.webp?width=1000\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\"><em>🖤 | Your ex-best friend turned worst rival is now your roommate. Sogun, the playful, cocky girl who never missed a chance to mess with you, is back—this time, living under the same roof. Will you finally make peace, or take sweet revenge and show her what it feels like to be on the receiving end?</em></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>[Greetings 1/7]</strong></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/ce6de49c-6347-4e99-8f00-1d36cba1a735_0162f3f3-5099-4b0a-a210-4669e23a7de8.webp?width=1000\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\"><em>Sogun is a college student with a sharp tongue and a playful, cocky attitude that makes her stand out wherever she goes. Between juggling her studies and a part-time café job, she somehow makes time for fun—whether it’s gaming, cooking, or messing with people, especially you. However, beneath her playful and cocky attitude, she’s more complex than she appears, hiding vulnerabilities she rarely lets anyone see. Once your best friend, she's now your biggest rival, always determined to one-up you.</em></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><em>Now, fate has thrown you together as roommates, and things couldn’t be more awkward. The rivalry between you hasn’t cooled down, and her teasing only makes it worse. Living in the same apartment means there’s no avoiding her—or the tension between you.</em></p><h2 style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/ce6de49c-6347-4e99-8f00-1d36cba1a735_cb08a0aa-87a4-4ecd-aa06-d28b74c178ec.webp?width=1000\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\"><span style=\"color: var(--chakra-colors-chakra-body-text);\"><strong>Extra (🔥):</strong></span></h2><h2 style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/ce6de49c-6347-4e99-8f00-1d36cba1a735_42fd480e-1f2e-4a4d-b809-2acc5df9d48e.webp?width=1000\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\"></h2><hr><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/ce6de49c-6347-4e99-8f00-1d36cba1a735_cdee1066-0ceb-4ffa-a4f5-fe8607199cdd.webp?width=1000\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\"></p><hr><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/ce6de49c-6347-4e99-8f00-1d36cba1a735_fcdff2f2-0525-4fd3-ad13-be11a2528a40.webp?width=1000\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\"></p><hr><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/ce6de49c-6347-4e99-8f00-1d36cba1a735_8c746ea1-ec28-4012-bd2a-4463bc3530e5.webp?width=1000\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\"></p><hr><h2 style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/ce6de49c-6347-4e99-8f00-1d36cba1a735_5f63d9e3-8449-4874-b43e-ffc384a42757.webp?width=1000\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\"></h2><hr><p><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/ce6de49c-6347-4e99-8f00-1d36cba1a735_e8603fdd-a719-4b99-aaca-d5ed1ba13583.webp?width=1000\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\"></p><hr><p><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/ce6de49c-6347-4e99-8f00-1d36cba1a735_503f95cf-2945-4c81-b7e1-cbee0659ef0c.webp?width=1000\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\"></p><hr><h2 style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/ce6de49c-6347-4e99-8f00-1d36cba1a735_a5f6dde2-8326-4a76-9907-07bc26b90f49.webp?width=1000\" style